	Holmes heels    
	London, Dec. 1: Actress Katie Holmes has defended her decision to dress her 3-year-old daughter Suri Cruise in high heels, reports The Daily Telegraph.      
	Parenting forums have criticised Holmes and her husband, Tom Cruise, for dressing the little girl in inappropriate footwear.      
	Suri is regularly photographed wearing silver or gold kitten heels on shopping trips with her mother. Speaking to Access Hollywood, Holmes said the heels did Suri no harm. Like every little girl, she loves my high heels, she said.      
	 the Mumsnet website, mothers of toddlers disagreed. Am I over-reacting or am I right in thinking that celebs should not be leading the way in sexualising children? asked one.                                                                                                                                                           
